es about us mission vision  values corporate strategy capabilities sustainability acquisition strategy management team board of directors culture  careers history watts water in action global operations americas europe asiapacific middle east  africa watts water in action watts brings clean water to kids in the philippines read more a long history watts water technologies inc has a long history the company was founded by joseph e watts in  under the name watts regulator company watts regulator started as a small machine shop supplying parts to the new england textile mills including manufacturing pressurereducing and relief valves to ensure the safe operation of water heaters and boilers breadth  depth today watts water through its subsidiaries is a global provider of plumbing heating and water quality solutions for residential industrial municipal and commercial settings our family of companies offers one of the most varied plumbing heating and water quality product lines in the world we offer a wide range of worldclass waterrelated solutions focused on plumbing  flow control water quality  conditioning water reuse  drainage hvac municipal waterworks global presence we have a global presence from our corporate headquarters in north andover ma to key business subsidiaries in the americas emea and asiapacific in addition the watts water technologies inc executive team brings together a significant depth and breadth of management experience strategic goals watts water is traded on the new york stock exchange under the symbol “wts” as a public company growing shareholder value is critical to that end we focus on a fivepart global strategy growth commercial excellence operational excellence “one watts water” and a talent  performance culture we are watts water technologies virtual tour take a virtual tour of a typical residential and commercial building and explore watts water technologies product applications watts water technologies  culture  careers watts water technologies culture  careers job search career opportunities search our us job openings online access for global opportunies will be available soon search jobs about watts water a long history the company was founded by joseph e watts in  under the name watts regulator company learn more culture and careers at watts water at watts water our culture is reflective of our mission vision and values our career opportunities are ideally suited for candidates who can identify with our goals  objectives and demonstrate the skills  abilities reflected in our core competencies to attract those highquality individuals we offer a competitive benefits package and opportunities for growth core competencies at watts water we are committed to attracting developing and promoting talented people who help create value for our customers and shareholders we use  core competencies to evaluate potential associates and assess the performance of our current staff these core competencies are a direct reflection of our belief that a solid understanding of what’s expected will lead to stronger job performance and satisfaction we expect all of our associates to demonstrate their ability and willingness to collaborate across workgroups communicate effectively deliver highquality work drive for results focus on the customer initiate positive change virtual tour take a virtual tour of a typical residential and commercial building and explore watts water technologies product applications watts water technologies  contact us watts water technologies contact us about watts water a long history the company was founded by joseph e watts in  under the name watts regulator company learn more watts water in action watts brings clean water to kids in the philippines read more americas and corporate headquarters watts water technologies inc americas headquarters  chestnut street north andover ma  usa p     f     europe watts water technologies inc europe headquarters strawinskylaan   zx amsterdam p      f      